# Themify Icons

@https://themify.me/themify-icons

## Usage

- Use `<i class="ti-{name}"></i>` for all icons
- Browse the full icon set at the reference URL above

## Common Icons

| Icon | Class |
|------|-------|
| Home | `ti-home` |
| User | `ti-user` |
| Settings | `ti-settings` |
| Search | `ti-search` |
| Menu | `ti-menu` |
| Close | `ti-close` |
| Arrow Left | `ti-arrow-left` |
| Arrow Right | `ti-arrow-right` |
| Check | `ti-check` |
| Plus | `ti-plus` |
| Trash | `ti-trash` |
| Pencil | `ti-pencil` |
| Eye | `ti-eye` |
| Lock | `ti-lock` |
| Bell | `ti-bell` |

## Guidelines

- Do **not** mix with other icon libraries (Font Awesome, Material Icons, etc.) unless explicitly requested
- Size icons with Bootstrap utility classes (`fs-4`, `fs-5`) or custom font-size when needed
- Apply color with Bootstrap text utilities (`text-primary`, `text-danger`, etc.)
